      "id": "PopularPost228907",
      "post_content": "This is a \"properly balanced\" card. In today's casual games you are either sacrificing creatures to punish your opponent (through cards like [Gravepact](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gravepact) and such) or so your opponent cannot take control of them.   \n  \nIn the latter case, [Culling Dias](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Culling Dias) is generally superior.",
